{"tid":1456893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入機場坐下，又無犯法，點解要走？","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:56.000Z","uid":258217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0844fda97c97163a585c687f41d731ff79576ef3","tid":1456893,"uid":258217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"其實政府又成功左少少，就係要你驚<br />\n驚到狗影都未見到就自己散水<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地依家無做錯任何野，唔洗咁快心虛走定先喎</span></span><br />\n航班復飛啦，但人又走晒，琴日講到背水一戰咁原來自己呃自己？<br />\n你去得機班就係想用和理非方法抗爭，但做完又要驚，不停自我設限<br />\n<br />\n唯一要驚就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有鬼搞事</span>，一有人搞事，比d勇氣㩒低佢，好無？"},{"pid":"19915333163a5242caff4073264d9caa4df46cf0","tid":1456893,"uid":258217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5644d79fffa633a42b20a8a0b8cc4f5ef52519f","tid":1456893,"uid":258217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:59:37.000Z","msg":"自己諗下你驚d乜"},{"pid":"573623f00d09d41d912a5e9fce90f63cf6544ff9","tid":1456893,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇犯法<br />\n驚閪咩</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c2eea7d18f9e5e78e56bc8dff38ddbf26d9d5d5e","tid":1456893,"uid":302005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"你唔走佔領個機場做乜柒？再講，dllm警方打你使撚理由，你着得黑衫戴得口罩出黎，佢肯撚定打死你"},{"pid":"5e4c4d26e2ba29f317561cf079221265ec02d083","tid":1456893,"uid":215844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2eea7d18f9e5e78e56bc8dff38ddbf26d9d5d5e","tid":1456893,"uid":302005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"你唔走佔領個機場做乜柒？再講，dllm警方打你使撚理由，你着得黑衫戴得口罩出黎，佢肯撚定打死你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"屌你都廢時"}]}